<br>
Why? Regardless, of what any magician says.  It is still the most powerful pet in the game. Period.  In game, if you take a look at the damage comparisons between the 59 necromancer pet and any mage pet you'll see that there is in fact a considerable difference in damage, (with or without damage-shields/augmentation of death).<br>
<br>
As far as damage avioidance is concerned.  Giving root/mez/charm to a magician completely negates their role entirely.  There is a reason for that. <br>
<br>
To Livinth:  At the moment..Dire Charm isn't work as it is intended. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
