<br>
<br>
Like Deke says the class balancing sucks bad in the game and is only getting further apart...I also think people missed the point on the Mage epic. Its extremely difficult to get and most guilds wont put the effort into getting a mage his epic. I would like to see epic quests be a little more balanced..why does one class need so many trips to a plain in hopes they will get a random epic piece while others get static spawns and camps that can easily be done with a few groups and maybe need a guild raid for the &quot;final epic&quot; battle.<br>
<br>
Nerfing Dire Charm would be silly. It takes a hell of a lot time and energy to even get the skill. /pet hold here is BS and should just be implemeted into any pet playing class from lvl 1..we are after all master of pets!<br>
<br>
<br>
